data.description: Fantastic 3 Bedroom, 1 Bathroom Ranch home tucked perfectly within a quite, established neighborhood on a dead-end street. The updated kitchen offers new tile and glass backsplash, countertops with custom cabinets. Brand New Luxury Vinyl Plank flooring installed 8/23 throughout the kitchen and entryway. Brand New Carpet and waterproof pad installed 8/23 in the living room and bedrooms. Utility room offers a large area for additional storage or pantry space. Complete Roof, Decking and Gutters Replaced in 2021. Enjoy entertaining on the 14x24 concrete patio with plenty of room for outdoor games within the fenced and level backyard.
